CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, April 7, 1956, page 16, reads: "...8. Gorgeous Mrs. Esther Austin poses atop the exquisite 1956 Dodge convertible in the Mount Lebanon Motors, Dodge dealers, booth..."
TitMainTitle: Esther Austin seated on back of Dodge convertible, in Syria Mosque for the 1956 Pittsburgh Courier Home Service Fair
